<br>
The new DW changes are all aggro-based. Perhaps Mythic thought our anytime damage waally was OK, but they were aware that we got toasted every time we got aggro, or something. Whatever, we have abominable defense to make up for our lack of a shield.<br>
<br>
It seems that the new changes are only gonna be any good in a merc with high parry. However, at least Mythic seems to be validating their original advice on how to spec a merc, which, I'll grudgingly admit, I am not respeccing to.<br>
