You mentioned 50, 39, 39... actually you can take it higher <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   I think you can go 50, 40, 41 or higher, if you level out.<br>
